<p><span class="anchor" id="p4"></span><span class="c2">(٢)</span> Sudarabische Sage Uber die: A.V.Kremer ليبسك ١٨٦٦، ص ٧٠ وما بعدها.<a href="#p4" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p5"></span><span class="c2">(٣)</span> - chichte des Alexanderromans, Denks Beitrage zur Ges-: Noldeke. chriften der Kais. Akademie der Wis- senschaften (Phil-Hist. Klasse, ٣٨ senschaften (Phil-Hist. Klasse, ٣٨.-.vol.,)Wlen ١٨٩٠ v. Abhandlung.<a href="#p5" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
